Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.80,0:01:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十三集\N向横纲迈进！\N虎丸的相扑奋战记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘 这个好重喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要一次买这么多吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是一起买比较省事嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正放着又不会坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.89,0:02:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说家里有两个大饭桶\N一下了就会吃光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉！当穷人真累！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀！千大人！好帅喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是花大关 真有人缘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大关…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗？剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人叫千两山 刚当上大关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他晋升到横纲是迟早的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千两山大关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你抱抱我孙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能长得白白壮壮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.76,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要！好可怕啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.50,0:02:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这么爱哭\N就不能像千两这么强壮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！有人吃东西不付钱啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从练习所逃跑后\N现在又白吃白喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！师兄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.82,0:03:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢人现眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少在那装疯卖傻\N有没有听到我说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.53,0:03:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风车！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来！我们走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是白吃白喝的无赖\N也是有他的长处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是没骨气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使对方是大关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自己也是个相扑手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来教训教训你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少说废话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饶…饶命啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你们！就放过他吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.57,0:03:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么样他只有一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.13,0:03:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们一群人\N打一个不觉得太过份了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少管闲事\N小丫头闪到一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么？可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.82,0:04:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也同意薰姑娘的说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！你以为我们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！竟敢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逃之夭夭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！这个混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都给我住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.66,0:04:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只有一个人\N就算打赢也胜之不武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是大关…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸尝过这次教训后\N应该会跑去躲起来了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.42,0:05:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸有时会和千两山大关\N一起到我店里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他和我很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为何要逃离相扑练习所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.43,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是生性懦弱\N没有耐性 这还用问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是师兄千两山大关\N能力强形象又好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被逼得受不了逃掉的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没得吃才白吃白喝吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.35,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千两山大关因能力强受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使为所欲为也没人会抱怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们常喝醉又打破东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.66,0:05:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近店里名声并不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想自杀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是虎丸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管他 别管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.14,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种胆小鬼没胆自杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以不管！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别拉我！让我死！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.62,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我这么没志气\N又没用 不如一死了之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.02,0:06:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你别拉我 唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跳啊！啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰…薰姑娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦！剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这条河水很浅的啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件和服今天才第一次穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们该不会是前世情末了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.85,0:06:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连投水自杀都能遇上大小姐\N你也太博爱了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.66,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真搞不懂丑女的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.06,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是丑女啊？丑…哈啾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.77,0:07:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回乡下老家只会麻烦到家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在想不到其他办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.77,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也不能寻死啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.34,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就多吃点打起精神来嘛！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！好丰盛的一餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先警告你 阿薰煮的饭很难吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.49,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近进步多了 现在比较能咽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正吃了不会死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说话客气点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！好久没吃到\N这么多又好吃的饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀！你真的觉得好吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有你识货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不要客气 多吃一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！真是好吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,食量可真惊人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光食量就像横纲级人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说虎丸\N千两山好像常常欺负你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师兄他人比较严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终究我是技不如人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初在乡下相扑我还很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.67,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想当上横纲才上京城来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是来了东京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才知道自己一无是处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.55,0:08:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不想再继续相扑了吗 虎丸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！像这种胆小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再练几年也是没希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总比你的剑术有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的个性比你率直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.87,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连我做的饭都说好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是令我感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.64,0:08:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了！虎丸 我来帮你训练好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？训练？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说相扑训练啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正相扑和剑术大同小异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.75,0:09:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是神谷活心派的大师\N一切就包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.09,0:09:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会想教\N虎丸相扑的技巧吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐你该不会是认真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来！虎丸多吃点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！真好吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘 那我们也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸 腰再用力一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了！就这样再做两百下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！要做这么多啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘真的很认真在训练耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.23,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！真是个严格的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.07,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸聪明的话最好现在就快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不行了 薰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个比练习所的训练还要严格啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.91,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就说不行怎能变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你乡下的父母正满心期待\N你当上横纲唷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.36,0:10:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸要努力当上横纲\N我们来为你加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸要当上横纲喔！加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连小绫小雀都来为我加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了！薰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能捏一下我的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.64,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我母亲常这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.25,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！虎丸 那我就不客气喽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太用力了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.79,0:10:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.09,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘我觉得\N精神好像好起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！虎丸打起精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.22,0:11:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！再做一段！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！唷咿啾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个样子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姐姐！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带饭团给你们吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给虎丸的有这么大喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思！小雀 小绫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们来吃午饭吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？大关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.99,0:12:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸那混蛋\N现在住在剑术道场里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦！不想相扑想当剑术家啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.99,0:12:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑也要有限度啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是！他是在道场里练习相扑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.63,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父听到这件事后说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果虎丸还想练相扑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是允许他回练习所来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.28,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父干嘛要偏袒那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎么了？大关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在马上去找虎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.29,0:12:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 我们走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千两山他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.60,0:12:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！刚刚在道场附近\N鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上好像杀气腾腾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了这阵子的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 不好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.48,0:13:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿妙有事情要告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸人在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.15,0:13:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在和薰姑娘在神社练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的饭团特别好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剑哥哥做的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑哥哥很会做饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.44,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么\N我都捏不好三角？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为薰姐姐很不会做饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说虎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使师父原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会原谅你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要想再回练习所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只会破坏我们的名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！你们想对虎丸怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.66,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦逃离练习所\N我决不让你再练相扑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理 虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你带小绫她们先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想逃 哇！好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个八婆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.61,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别欺人太甚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.88,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我是女的\N敢欺负我 就要你好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.15,0:14:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少说大话！哇！好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.26,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他给逃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘！唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小绫！小雀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个过气剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿！相扑和剑术一比高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明神祢彦来也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要留情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我解决掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！相扑就要有相扑的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要赤手空拳打才行啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下我可生气了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在！揍扁他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.73,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都退开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.78,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.51,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还想修理我们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.79,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这伙人到底是什么来头？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千两山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不放过虎丸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.77,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！那家伙是我们滨风练习所的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.61,0:16:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要问的是真正的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.18,0:16:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话！还有什么真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正跟你没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.52,0:16:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别搞错了 你的对手是虎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.92,0:16:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸怎会是大关的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚保护我的时候\N虎丸真的很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸如果你认真的话\N一定没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我只是一时情急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈！\N虎丸 如果是你 我随时奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！要当上横纲喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我脚动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你要干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.59,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！打起精神 我捏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰姑娘 小绫 小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩！那你站稳了！来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！稳住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.89,0:17:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唷咿咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.36,0:17:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇喔啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.96,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！这家伙开窍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.63,0:18:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸赢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.90,0:18:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕的就是这个吧！千两山！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师…师父！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.81,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能当上大关\N应该已看出虎丸潜在的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是曾几何时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.95,0:18:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开始担心师弟\N会威胁到你的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.46,0:18:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸该不会真的很强吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前他被千两山揍时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.06,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体就轻巧地闪开风车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.04,0:18:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚为了保护薰姑娘\N也能一口气挡开石灯笼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.01,0:19:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他具有成大器的能耐\N只是自己不知道而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然没看走眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.72,0:19:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我看人很准的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.02,0:19:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿！祢彦 这下服气了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.12,0:19:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可真是玉不琢不成器啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不算晚\N你就回练习所来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.00,0:19:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太谢谢你了！师父！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.71,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有千两山你这丢脸的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.61,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千两山你现在已是大关\N还好没铸成大错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.32,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后要堂堂正正在相扑场上\N与虎丸比个高下喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滨风师父 您意下如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我就此原谅千两山？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了虎丸这样比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相扑和打斗一样\N没有强劲对手就无法变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.44,0:20:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！师兄！我想再努力试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.75,0:20:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后还要麻烦你多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.33,0:20:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才一阵子没见\N你看起来进步不少 虎丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎丸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是说人人就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.88,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会\N又从练习所逃出来了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦！我现在很努力练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.22,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想到前阵子很麻烦你们\N今天买了米当谢礼送来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！我们正好缺米呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀！
